              <h1>What Is Deliverado?</h1>
              <h4>Deliverado is a shuttle service for goods, purchased from the Media Markt and Saturn e-shops, with the focus on same-day delivery!
              </h4>

              <h4>For the delivery of the goods mainly the daily commuter traffic is used to use synergies, to save costs and to protect the environment.</h4>
